Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}お前なら知っているはずだ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}你应该心知肚明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.51,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}生臭坊主め
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}臭和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}そこまで調べていたのか
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}竟然查得这么深入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.19,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}まずは大きな木を探そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.19,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}先找比较大的树吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}大きな木か
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.90,0:13:56.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}大树吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}途方もないな
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}没头绪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.32,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}たくさんあるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.82,0:14:00.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:04.57,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}まぁ、時間なんていくらでもあるのか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.03,0:14:04.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}反正时间要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.49,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}まぁね
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}でもフェルンが嫌がるから
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}可是菲伦会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.50,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}早めに終わらせようか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.50,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}还是抓紧时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}なるべく効率的に探しましょう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}尽量高效地寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}変わったな
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:24.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}お前は人の時間を気にするようなヤツじゃなかった
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.80,0:14:24.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}你以前可不会在时间上顾虑别人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.10,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}だってフェルン、怒ると怖いんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.30,0:14:28.10,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}因为菲伦生起气来很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.68,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&F2F2F2}{\bord2.5}そうか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.68,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&F2F2F2}{\bord2.5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.85,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&F2F2F2}{\bord2.5}気を付けよう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&F2F2F2}{\bord2.5}要当心了
