Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.76,0:15:11.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&666666\4c&666666}{\c&E6E6E6}{\bord2.5}西边有一棵吞没了遗迹的大树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.23,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&666666\4c&666666}{\c&E6E6E6}{\bord2.5}こちらです
