Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&BFB7AC}{\bord2.5}かわいそうだと思ってな
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}{\c&BFB7AC}{\bord2.5}因为某人很可怜
