Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\c&E4F2EE}芙莉莲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:30.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\c&E4F2EE}大樹も遺跡も強力な結界で守られていて
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.67,0:16:30.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\c&E4F2EE}大树和遗迹都被强大的结界保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.56,Dial-JPN,,2033,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D1E0DF}1000年も前のことなのに
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.56,Dial-CHI,,2033,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D1E0DF}都过了一千年了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.35,Dial-JPN,,2033,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D1E0DF}結局私は先生の手のひらの上か
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.35,Dial-CHI,,2033,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&D1E0DF}我还是逃不出老师的手心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}頼りない留守番だね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}这守卫靠不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.11,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}そうでもねえさ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}{\c&E6E6E6}话不能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.66,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&666666\4c&666666}{\c&E6E6E6}{\bord2.5}こいつが成長すれば
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&666666\4c&666666}{\c&E6E6E6}{\bord2.5}它只要长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:52.82,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\3c&666666\4c&666666}{\c&E6E6E6}{\bord2.5}1000年だろうがこの場所を守り続ける
