Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.79,Dial-CHI,,1999,0,0,,{\be1}{\3c&998C6E\4c&998C6E}{\bord1}你将来一定会犯下大错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.46,Dial-JPN,,1999,0,0,,{\be1}{\3c&998C6E\4c&998C6E}{\bord1}人を知りたいと考えるようになる
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.46,Dial-CHI,,1999,0,0,,{\be1}{\3c&998C6E\4c&998C6E}{\bord1}然后变得渴望了解人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:08.09,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}知ってほしいの、先生
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.88,0:17:08.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}您希望我了解你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.22,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}かまってちゃん?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}缺爱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:10.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}違ぇよ
